y%20some%20are%20turning%20back%20to%20travel%20agents.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20number%20of%20travel%20agents%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vice.com%2Fen%2Farticle%2F8q8q4p%2Fwhy-are-travel-agents-still-a-thing-internet-airlines-agencies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalf%20of%20what%20it%20was%20at%20the%20industry's%20mid-'90s%20peak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20many%20expecting%20it%20to%20become%20obsolete.%20But%20by%202021%2C%2076%25%20of%20advisors%20were%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F04%2F14%2Ftravel%2Fsummer-vacation-travel-agents.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20before%20the%20pandemic.%20And%20in%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibsplc.com%2Fnews%2Fsurvey-surprising-trends-among-the-youngest-travelers-as-47-of-americans-turn-toward-travel-agents-to-book-their-holiday-travel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%202%2C000%20American%20travelers%2C%2038%25%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennial%20respondents%20said%20they%20preferred%20a%20traditional%20travel%20agent%20over%20online%20booking.%20Only%2012%25%20of%20Gen%20Xers%20and%202%25%20of%20boomers%20said%20the%20same.%20Whether%20we're%20bopping%20around%20the%20Mediterranean%20or%20just%20posting%20up%20at%20an%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico%20for%20a%20week%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20are%20deciding%20we'd%20rather%20put%20the%20planning%20in%20someone%20else's%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20James%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20software%20engineer%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20was%20initially%20excited%20to%20plan%20his%20summer%20trip%20to%20Vietnam%20himself.%20Like%20many%20his%20age%2C%20he's%20primarily%20interested%20in%20sightseeing%20in%20cities.%20%26quot%3BI%20found%20myself%20going%20down%20hourslong%20internet%20rabbit%20holes%20trying%20to%20hone%20in%20on%20a%20perfect%20itinerary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGoogling%20'best%20neighborhoods%20in%20Hanoi%20Reddit%2C'%20'two-week%20Vietnam%20itinerary%20Reddit%2C'%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20while%2C%20though%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20find%20the%20time%20and%20energy%20to%20plan.%20Doing%20his%20own%20research%20was%20mentally%20exhausting.%20He%20decided%20to%20give%20up%20the%20hunt%20and%20hand%20the%20work%20over%20to%20a%20travel%20advisor%20who%20was%20also%20a%20family%20friend.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20able%20to%20take%20care%20of%20booking%20visas%2C%20flights%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20a%20few%20excursions%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20tempting%20to%20have%20him%20take%20care%20of%20it%20all%20in%20one%20email%20thread%20for%20a%20couple-hundred-dollar%20fee.%26quot%3B%20Now%2C%20he%20said%2C%20all%20that's%20left%20is%20deciding%20what%20to%20see%20and%20eat%20at%20each%20location%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20lets%20him%20satisfy%20his%20urge%20to%20rabbit-hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Business%20Insider%20survey%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20YouGov%2C%20millennials%20cited%20travel%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-choose-travel-over-promotions-paying-off-debt-2023-12%3Futm_source%3Dreddit%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dinsider-Millennials-sub-post%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20their%20most%20important%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20more%20important%20than%20having%20fulfilling%20romantic%20relationships%2C%20owning%20a%20home%2C%20advancing%20their%20career%2C%20or%20starting%20a%20family.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20only%20two%20goals%20millennials%20considered%20more%20important%20than%20traveling%20were%20being%20financially%20stable%20and%20improving%20their%20health.%20Amid%20rising%20costs%20for%20housing%2C%20childcare%2C%20and%20everything%20else%2C%20key%20milestones%20get%20pushed%20further%20down%20the%20road.%20A%20flight%20to%20Mexico%20City%20and%20five%20nights%20at%20a%20boutique%20hotel%20in%20Coyoac%C3%A1n%2C%20however%2C%20feels%20a%20little%20more%20firmly%20within%20our%20grasp.%20In%20a%202023%20Morning%20Consult%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F04%2F17%2Fgen-z-travel-trends-travel-often-save-money-and-seek-adventure-.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20both%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%20were%20more%20likely%20than%20older%20generations%20to%20travel%20frequently%2C%20with%20half%20of%20each%20cohort%20saying%20they%20took%20three%20or%20more%20leisure%20trips%20a%20year.%20Gen%20Zers%20were%20also%20more%20likely%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F04%2F17%2Fgen-z-travel-trends-travel-often-save-money-and-seek-adventure-.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20overseas%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20their%20older%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20as%20little%20as%20%24100%20%E2%80%94%20or%20nothing%20at%20all%2C%20given%20that%20some%20agents%20work%20on%20commission%20from%20the%20hotels%20and%20other%20travel%20companies%20they%20work%20with%20%E2%80%94%20overwhelmed%20young%20travelers%20can%20have%20someone%20take%20all%20the%20pressure%20off%20the%20experience.%20There%20are%20travel%20agents%20specializing%20in%20just%20about%20every%20type%20of%20travel%20imaginable%2C%20from%20multicountry%20group%20tours%20to%20luxury%20all-inclusive%20trips.%20And%20different%20types%20of%20agents%20can%20offer%20different%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20complex%20overseas%20trips%2C%20where%20a%20million%20things%20could%20go%20wrong%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20hire%20an%20agent%20to%20not%20only%20ensure%20everything%20goes%20as%20smoothly%20as%20possible%20but%20also%20handle%20the%20rebookings%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20hiccup.%20When%20something%20goes%20awry%2C%20it's%20someone%20else's%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20James%20decided%20to%20have%20his%20agent%20handle%20just%20the%20basics%20of%20his%20Vietnam%20vacation%2C%20many%20agents%20can%20help%20curate%20the%20experiences%20in%20between%2C%20promising%20to%20find%20their%20clients%20the%20coolest%20markets%20to%20shop%20at%20or%20the%20most-recommended%20museums.%20On%20a%20different%20trip%2C%20to%20Oktoberfest%20in%20Germany%2C%20James'%20travel%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20a%20native%20German%20speaker%20%E2%80%94%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20all%20sorts%20of%20reservations%20that%20James%20would%20never%20have%20been%20able%20to%20land%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasingly%2C%20travel%20agents%20are%20luring%20people%20in%20through%20social%20media%2C%20where%20they%20can%20speak%20straight%20to%20the%20millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20desire%20for%20a%20unique%20experience%20and%20a%20relaxing%20trip.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20give%20you%20the%20special%20slice-of-life%20experience%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20pitch%2C%20%26quot%3Bjust%20without%20the%20hassle.%26quot%3B%20Companies%20like%20Fora%2C%20for%20example%2C%20use%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%20to%20seed%20sleek%20ads%20for%20package%20trips%20to%20the%20Croatian%20coast%20or%20boutique%20hotels%20in%20the%20Florida%20Keys%2C%20with%20extra%20attention%20given%20to%20%26quot%3Bsustainability%26quot%3B%20and%20travelers'%20specific%20%26quot%3Baesthetic%26quot%3B%20desires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgents%20elsewhere%20on%20TikTok%20tout%20all-inclusive%20trips%20where%20the%20point%20is%20to%20just%20lie%20on%20the%20beach%20and%20chill%20the%20hell%20out%20for%20a%20second.%20Searches%20for%20topics%20like%20%26quot%3Bbest%20all-inclusives%20Canc%C3%BAn%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40thetropicaltravelers%2Fvideo%2F7205590968710548778%3Fq%3Dbest%2520riviera%2520maya%2520all%2520inclusive%26t%3D1714160542049%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavily%20feature%20travel%20agents%20promoting%20their%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ranking%20their%20favorite%20resorts%20and%20highlighting%20the%20perks%20they%20can%20offer%20clients%20who%20book%20with%20them.%20One%20of%20their%20main%20selling%20points%3A%20Their%20services%20are%20free.%20And%20many%20agents%20also%20claim%20that%20their%20customers%20can%20receive%20better%20deals%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40iamtiffanydionne%2Fvideo%2F7163316542011100462%3Fq%3Dperks%2520of%2520using%2520a%2520travel%2520agent%26t%3D1717955726864%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethanks%20to%20the%20special%20pricing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20perks%20available%20to%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20my%20Gen%20Z%20clients%20are%20in%20entry-level%20careers%2C%20graduate%20programs%2C%20or%20saving%20for%20other%20big%20expenses%2C%20so%20they're%20often%20looking%20for%20destinations%20that%20allow%20them%20to%20relax%20while%20making%20the%20most%20of%20their%20limited%20vacation%20days%20and%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kayla%20Smith%2C%20a%20travel%20advisor%20for%20Sojourney%20Travel%2C%20a%20company%20specializing%20in%20beach%20vacations%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20theme-park%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20is%20a%20Gen%20Zer%20and%20said%20that%20over%20half%20her%20clients%20are%20Gen%20Z.%20%26quot%3BGoing%20from%20school%20to%20the%20workforce%20is%20already%20a%20huge%20life%20transition%2C%20and%20when%20you%20add%20on%20a%20pandemic%20and%20varying%20career%20expectations%2C%20you're%20bound%20to%20see%20a%20generation%20who%20is%20experiencing%20burnout%20at%20a%20rapid%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20reason%2C%20resort%20groups%20like%20Sandals%20are%20seeing%20an%20influx%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials.%20Ashley%20Kooker%2C%20a%20senior%20business-development%20manager%20for%20Unique%20Vacations%2C%20a%20sales%20and%20marketing%20affiliate%20of%20Sandals%20and%20Beaches%20Resorts%2C%20said%20that%20these%20properties%20had%20been%20attracting%20younger%20customers%20in%20part%20by%20blending%20the%20all-inclusive%20format%20with%20the%20opportunity%20for%20more%20exploration.%20At%20Sandals%20Royal%20Curacao%20and%20Sandals%20Royal%20Bahamian%2C%20guests%20can%20opt%20to%20go%20off-resort%20and%20visit%20local%20restaurants%20as%20part%20of%20their%20all-inclusive%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20experience-minded%20vacationers%20to%20have%20their%20cake%20and%20eat%20it%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EExhaustion%20aside%2C%20many%20of%20us%2020-somethings%20still%20yearn%20for%20these%20hard-to-get-to%2C%20out-of-the-box%20journeys%20%E2%80%94%20the%20trips%20that%20make%20us%20feel%20like%20travelers%20rather%20than%20tourists.%20William%20Lee%2C%20a%20travel%20agent%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchima.travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChima%20Travel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20family-owned%20agency%20in%20Ohio%20that's%20been%20operating%20for%20over%20100%20years%2C%20told%20me%20he%20often%20gets%20requests%20for%20obscure%20destinations%20young%20clients%20see%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20client%20come%20in%20and%20ask%20us%20about%20Oeschinen%20Lake%20in%20Switzerland%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20saw%20the%20lake%20on%20TikTok%20and%20wanted%20to%20go%20there.%20I%20had%20to%20let%20them%20know%20that%20to%20do%20so%20would%20require%20hiking%20into%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%20and%20going%20a%20bit%20off%20the%20beaten%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20wrapped%20up%20a%2010-day%20trip%20to%20Peru%2C%20where%20I%20hiked%20for%20three%20days%20through%20the%20Lares%20District%2C%20ate%20quinoa%20soup%20in%20the%20San%20Pedro%20Market%20in%20Cusco%2C%20and%20bar-hopped%20in%20Lima.%20It%20was%20a%20trip%20packed%20with%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20the%20kind%20that%20my%20generation%20is%20always%20talking%20about%20prioritizing%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20I%20relaxed%20for%20a%20moment.%20And%20that's%20despite%20leaving%20all%20the%20planning%20to%20my%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20already%20plotting%20my%20next%20big%2C%20multiweek%20international%20trip%20%E2