ww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-jio-jv-gets-space-regulator-s-approval-to-operate-satellites-124061300417_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-jio-jv-gets-space-regulator-s-approval-to-operate-satellites-124061300417_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himachal's%20U-Turn%20On%20Providing%20Water%20To%20Parched%20Delhi%20Draws%20Top%20Court%20Rap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20twist%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20battle%20over%20Delhi's%20spiralling%20water%20crisis%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20has%20said%20it%20does%20not%20have%20surplus%20water%20to%20send%20to%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20hill%20state%20said%20it%20had%20released%20water%20for%20Delhi%20and%20the%20supply%20needs%20to%20go%20through%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Delhi%20residents%20reel%20under%20the%20double%20blow%20of%20a%20heatwave%20and%20water%20crisis%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20to%20release%20137%20cusecs%20of%20surplus%20water%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20told%20Haryana%20to%20facilitate%20its%20flow.%20The%20court%20had%20said%20the%20drinking%20water%20shortage%20has%20become%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20problem%26quot%3B%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%20yesterday%2C%20Himachal%20Chief%20Minister%20Sukhwinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20said%20the%20state%20has%20released%20water.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20released%20water.%20We%20have%20asked%20advocates%20to%20inform%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20about%20this.%20The%20water%20we%20have%20released%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20give%20that%20water.%20There%20are%20no%20ifs%20and%20buts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20U-turn%20today%2C%20Himachal%20government's%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%20today%20that%20the%20137%20cusecs%20water%20was%20%26quot%3Bunutilised%20after%20use%20of%20irrigation%20and%20part%20of%20natural%20course%20of%20river%20flow%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20not%20convey%20it%20properly%20earlier.%20Our%20correct%20statement%20may%20come%20on%20record.%20Maybe%20we%20made%20a%20mistake%20earlier%2C%20but%20I%20have%20been%20briefed.%20I%20will%20correct%20and%20withdraw%20the%20earlier%20statement%20that%20flow%20was%20obstructed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20drew%20a%20warning%20from%20the%20court.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20haul%20you%20up%20for%20contempt%20and%20summon%20your%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20The%20Himachal%20government%20counsel%20apologised%20and%20said%20they%20will%20submit%20an%20affidavit%20and%20withdraw%20their%20earlier%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20Upper%20River%20Yamuna%20Board%20to%20find%20a%20resolution%20to%20the%20problem.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20board%20had%20said%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20should%20prove%20it%20has%20been%20releasing%20137%20cusecs%20of%20unutilised%20water%20for%20Delhi%20after%20the%20court's%20June%206%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%20filed%20before%20the%20court%2C%20the%20board%20referred%20to%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20Haryana%20by%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%20which%20the%20hill%20state%20has%20said%20its%20share%20of%20unutilised%20water%20was%20already%20flowing%20uninterruptedly%20to%20the%20Hathnikund%20barrage%20and%20that%20Haryana%20should%20release%20it%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20above%20letter%2C%20the%20137%20cusec%20of%20unutilised%20water%20is%20already%20flowing%20uninterruptedly%20from%20the%20territory%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20to%20Tajewala%20(in%20Haryana).%20It%20therefore%20emerges%20that%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20is%20not%20releasing%20any%20additional%20water%20subsequent%20to%20the%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dated%2006.06.2024%20which%20could%20be%20measured%20by%20Upper%20Yamuna%20River%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20of%20several%20areas%20in%20Delhi%20are%20suffering%20due%20to%20the%20shortage%20of%20drinking%20water%20that%20has%20made%20the%20heatwave%20unbearable.%20Amid%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20activities%20of%20tanker%20mafia%20have%20compounded%20residents'%20problems.%20The%20court%20has%20pulled%20up%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government%20over%20wastage%20of%20water%20and%20tanker%20mafia%20and%20questioned%20what%20steps%20it%20has%20taken%20to%20counter%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20visuals%20on%20every%20channel%20that%20the%20tanker%20mafia%20is%20working%20in%20Delhi.%20What%20measures%20have%20you%20taken%20in%20this%20regard%3F%20What%20measures%20have%20you%20taken%20to%20control%20water%20waste%20coming%20through%20the%20two%20barrages%20if%20this%20is%20a%20recurring%20problem%3F%20Please%20show%20us%20what%20action%20or%20FIR%20have%20you%20lodged%20against%20tanker%20mafias%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20water%20minister%20Atishi%20has%20accused%20government%20officials%20of%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20water%20tankers%20without%20her%20knowledge%20and%20said%20this%20aided%20the%20tanker%20mafia.%20She%20has%20also%20written%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20and%20sought%20an%20inquiry%20into%20the%20alleged%20tie-up%20between%20senior%20officials%20and%20tanker%20mafia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20is%20hearing%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20petition%20that%20seeks%20a%20direction%20to%20Haryana%20to%20release%20surplus%20water%20provided%20by%20Himachal%20to%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20has%20rejected%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20charge.%20%26quot%3BHaryana%20is%20diligently%20fulfilling%20its%20commitment%20to%20provide%20water%20to%20Delhi.%20Haryana%20not%20only%20meets%20but%20exceeds%20its%20obligations%20in%20this%