20she%20did%20not%20have%20to%20pursue%20those%20offers%20unless%20she%20wanted%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20great%20grandfather%20Sarju%20Singh%20Ranaut%20was%20an%20MLA.%20So%20these%20offers%20were%20never%20too%20far%20away%20from%20my%20family.%20I%20was%20offered%20to%20join%20politics%20right%20after%20my%20debut%20film%20Gangster.%20My%20father%20and%20sister%20have%20also%20received%20similar%20offers%20over%20the%20years.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20approached%20to%20join%20politics.%20If%20I%20wasn't%20interested%20in%20this%2C%20I%20didn't%20really%20have%20to%20go%20through%20so%20much%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20balancing%20films%20and%20her%20political%20career%2C%20the%20Mandi%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20life%20of%20a%20politician%20was%20much%20%26quot%3Bharsher%26quot%3B%20than%20her%20life%20as%20a%20movie%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20harsh%20life%2C%20not%20like%20films.%20As%20a%20film%20actor%2C%20you%20go%20to%20sets%20and%20premieres%2C%20you%20are%20relaxed.%20We%20(actors)%20live%20a%20soft%20life.%20So%2C%20it%20took%20a%20long%20time%20for%20me%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20this%20life.%20This%20is%20a%20harsh%20life%2C%20just%20like%20doctors%2C%20where%20only%20troubled%20people%20come%20to%20see%20you.%20When%20you%20go%20to%20watch%20a%20film%2C%20you%20are%20very%20relaxed.%20But%2C%20politics%20is%20not%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20set%20out%20on%20this%20path%20after%20receiving%20guidance%20from%20her%20guru%2C%20Sadhguru%20Jaggi%20Vasudev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20guru%20said%20if%20you%20do%20what%20you%20love%20you%20are%20intelligent%20but%20if%20you%20do%20what%20is%20needed%2C%20you%20will%20become%20a%20genius%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20her%20switch%20to%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ranaut%20won%20the%20Mandi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20over%2074%2C000%20vote