e%20the%20allegations.%20Based%20on%20the%20committee's%20recommendations%2C%20the%20scorecards%20of%20the%20affected%20candidates%20will%20be%20cancelled%2C%20and%20a%20re-examination%20will%20be%20held%20for%20these%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20reaffirmed%20its%20decision%20not%20to%20halt%20the%20counselling%20process%20for%20NEET-UG%202024.%C2%A0%26quot%3BCounselling%20will%20proceed%20as%20scheduled%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20interruption.%20If%20the%20exam%20continues%2C%20everything%20else%20will%20proceed%20as%20well%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20cause%20for%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counselling%20for%20admissions%20into%20MBBS%2C%20BDS%2C%20and%20other%20courses%20will%20start%20on%20July%206%2C%20the%20Centre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2024%20lakh%20medical%20aspirants%20took%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20-%C2%A0an%20ultra-competitive%20entrance%20test%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%C2%A0conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20to%20be%20declared%20on%20June%2014%20but%20were%20announced%20on%20June%204%2C%20apparently%20because%20the%20answer%20sheets%20were%20evaluated%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20allegations%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20medical%20aspirants%20triggered%20protests%20and%20lawsuits%20in%20seven%20High%20Courts%20besides%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20students%20protested%20in%20Delhi%20on%20June%2010%20seeking%20an%20inquiry%2C%20and%20alleging%20that%2067%20students%20shared%20the%20top%20rank%20because%20of%20grace%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetitioners%20from%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bno%20defined%20logic%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20grace%20marks.%20The%20petitions%20cited%20%26quot%3Bstatistically%20impossible%26quot%3B%20marks%2C%20including%20students%20scoring%20the%20maximum%20-%20720%20of%20720.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E67%20students%20from%20one%20coaching%20centre%20secured%20perfect%20scores%2C%20the%20petitions%20pointed%20out.%20They%20also%20cited%20a%20provisional%20answer%20key%20released%20by%20the%20NTA%2C%20which%20was%20contested%20by%20over%2013%2C000%20students%20as%20the%20problem%20pointed%20to%20a%20different%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20dangers%20of%20cheating%20in%20a%20medical%20test%2C%20the%20petitions%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20field%20requires%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20and%20medical%20knowledge...%20cheating%20or%20using%20unfair%20means%20to%20pass%20an%20exam%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20competence%20and%20endanger%20lives%20of%20patients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20NTA%20over%20petitions%20seeking%20to%20cancel%20the%20results%20of%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20that%20simple...%20that%20because%20you%20have%20done%20it%20(held%20the%20exam)%20it%20is%20sacrosanct%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20told%20the%20NTA%2C%20%26quot%3BSanctity%20of%20(the%20examination)%20has%20been%20affected...%20so%20we%20need%20answers.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20today%20told%20the%20top%20court%3A%C2%A0%26quot%3BA%20committee%20was%20set%20up%20to%20review%20the%20results%20of%20more%20than%201%2C563%20NEET-UG%202024%20candidates%20who%20received%20'grace%20marks'%20due%20to%20time%20loss%20during%20the%20exam.%20The%20committee%20has%20decided%20to%20invalidate%20the%20scorecards%20of%20these%20candidates%2C%20who%20will%20now%20have%20the%20option%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20re-test.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20all%20petitions%2C%20including%20those%20seeking%20cancellation%20of%20NEET-UG%202024%20on%20account%20of%20the%