aking%20preparations%20for%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20people%20from%20Shirsuphal%20village%20in%20Baramati%2C%20the%20former%20Union%20minister%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Baramati%20constituency%20remained%20silent%20during%20the%20election%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20party%20functionaries%20used%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20people%20are%20silent%20and%20they%20are%20not%20speaking%20openly.%20I%20asked%20them%20not%20to%20worry%20and%20said%20that%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20expressing%20themselves%2C%20they%20will%20press%20the%20right%20button%20(of%20EVMs).%20And%20the%20same%20thing%20happened.%20When%20the%20EVMs%20were%20opened%2C%20the%20magic%20was%20seen%20as%20you%20people%20voted%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20stay%20united%20as%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20are%20just%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20state%20elections%20are%20taking%20place.%20Come%20what%20may%2C%20it%20will%20be%20my%20endeavour%20to%20take%20control%20of%20Maharashtra.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20must%20win%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20recalled%20that%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20for%20four%20terms%2C%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20defence%20minister%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20things%20can%20happen%20when%20your%20collective%20power%20is%20there.%20The%20issues%20you%20have%20put%20forth%20before%20me%2C%20I%20will%20try%20and%20resolve%20them.%20However%2C%20I%20cannot%20give%20assurances%20now%20because%20a%20different%20government%20is%20in%20place.%20But%20after%20four%20months%2C%20we%20can%20certainly%20resolve%20these%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20criticized%20Prime%20