es-on-posts-private-on-x-to-boost-engagement-on-platform-124061300321_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-makes-likes-on-posts-private-on-x-to-boost-engagement-on-platform-124061300321_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20IITs%20And%20Women%3A%20It's%20Not%20A%20Question%20Of%20Merit%2C%20But%20Access%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fop5svbp_iit-delhil2_625x300_09_December_22.jpg%3Fdownsize%3D562%253A413%26disabledm%3D1%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20for%20this%20year's%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology-Joint%20Entrance%20Examination%20(IIT-JEE)%20are%20out%2C%20and%20it%20is%20heartening%20to%20see%20that%20of%20the%2048%2C248%20students%20who%20have%20qualified%20for%20the%20test%2C%207%2C964%20candidates%20are%20girls.%20In%20the%20Advanced%20test%2C%20Ved%20Lahoti%20of%20IIT%20Delhi%20zone%20topped%20in%20the%20Common%20Rank%20List%20(CRL)%20with%20355%20out%20of%20360%20marks%2C%20while%20Gujarat's%20Dwija%20Patel%20in%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20zone%20was%20the%20top-ranked%20female%20candidate%20with%20CRL%207.%20She%20scored%20332%20marks.%20A%20total%20of%201%2C80%2C200%20candidates%20appeared%20in%20the%20two%20JEE%20Advanced%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScience%2C%20particularly%20engineering%2C%20has%20been%20a%20male-dominated%20domain%20for%20long%2C%20with%20the%20female%20population%20on%20IIT%20campuses%20being%20almost%20negligible.%20There%20have%20been%20improvements%20though.%20The%20number%20of%20female%20enrolments%20in%20IITs%20more%20than%20tripled%20from%20just%20995%20in%202017%20to%203%2C411%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Lopsided%20Field%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20by%20the%20sub-committee%20of%20the%20Joint%20Admission%20Board%20(JAB)%2C%20the%20advisory%20body%20in%20charge%20of%20admissions%20to%20IITs%2C%20found%20that%20in%202016%2C%20as%20many%20as%204%2C570%20girls%20cleared%20the%20JEE%20(Advanced)%20exam%20but%20only%20848%20were%20admitted%20to%20an%20IIT.%20This%20reflects%20that%20though%20women%20are%20in%20no%20way%20less%20meritorious%2C%20systemic%20societal%20biases%20forbid%20them%20from%20making%20it%20to%20these%20premier%20institutes.%20On%20an%20average%2C%20the%20ratio%20of%20male%20to%20female%20students%20on%20an%20IIT%20campus%20has%20been%20about%2010%3A1%2C%20despite%20women%20performing%20significantly%20well%20in%20JEE%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoaching%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20preparation%20for%20JEE.%20But%20a%20majority%20of%20girls%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20such%20facilities%20given%20the%20gender%20bias%20in%20families.%20Most%20parents%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20invest%20much%20in%20her%20education%2C%20let%20alone%20coaching.%20There%20are%20also%20other%20restrictions%20that%20are%20amplified%20for%20girls%2C%20say%2C%20geographical%20access%20to%20coaching%20centres%20and%20social%20restrictions.%20All%20this%20deprives%20them%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20under-representation%20of%20female%20students%20in%20IITs%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20in%202018%20introduced%20supernumerary%20seats%2C%20that%20is%2C%20seats%20over%20and%20above%20the%20sanctioned%20limit%20by%20the%20government.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20IIT%20admissions%20council%20decided%20to%20set%20aside%20800%20(14%25)%20additional%20seats%20for%20girls%20across%20the%2023%20IITs.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20numbers%20increased%20to%20946%20(17%25)%20female-only%20seats.%20Then%2C%20in%202021%2C%20the%20JAB%20decided%20to%20allow%20IITs%20to%20fix%20their%20female%20enrolment%20targets%20at%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%20admissions.%20Not%20only%20did%20most%20institutes%20fulfil%20this%20quota%2C%20many%20even%20managed%20to%20exceed%20it.%20In%202023%2C%20as%20many%20as%203%2C411%20female-only%20seats%20were%20allotted%2C%20while%2011%20female%20candidates%20got%20admission%20in%20the%20gender-neutral%20pool.%20The%20overall%20percentage%20of%20females%20in%20IITs%20was%2019.7%25%20-%20one%20in%20five%20students%20was%20a%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20IITs%20have%20also%20taken%20progressive%20steps%20in%20offering%20scholarships%2C%20addressing%20gender%20disparity%20on%20campus%2C%20conducting%20special%20sessions%20with%20parents%20of%20girl%20students%2C%20and%20conducting%20outreach%20programmes%20in%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIITs%2C%20or%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20even%20NITs%20%5BNational%20Institute%20of%20Technology%5D%2C%20are%20on%20their%20way%20to%20becoming%20gender-balanced%20with%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20females%20in%20these%20institutions.%20Getting%20admission%20to%20IITs%20has%20always%20been%20tough.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20become%20just%20a%20bit%20easy%20for%20girls%20now.%20This%20will%20encourage%20female%20students%20to%20try%20for%20IITs%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Anjali%20Sharma%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%2C%20Department%20of%20Architecture%20and%20Planning%2C%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Patna.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20myth%20that%20girls%20in%20engineering%20colleges%20are%20less%20meritorious.%20Most%20often%2C%20girls%20outperform%20boys%20in%20reality.%20They%20are%20more%20sincere%20and%20hardworking.%20Females%20from%20these%20institutes%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20among%20the%20best%20in%20the%20corporate%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Sarita%20Kumari%2C%20an%20MTech%20student%20of%20IIT%20Bombay%2C%20echoes%20these%20views.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20more%20women%20succeed%20in%20these%20prestigious%20programmes%20helps%20dismantle%20stereotypes%20and%20encourages%20young%20girls%20to%20enter%20male-dominated%20fields...%20Ultimately%2C%20more%20girls%20attending%20IITs%20improves%20gender%20parity%20and%20benefits%20society%20by%20empowering%20women%20to%20effect%20meaningful%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouthern%20Triumphs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20IIT%20Madras%20zone%20has%20registered%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20qualified%20candidates.%20Of%20its%2011%2C180%20candidates%2C%20145%20feature%20in%20the%20top%20500%3B%20four%20from%20the%20top%2010%20are%20also%20from%20here.%20The%20zone%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20IIT-Hyderabad%20zone-%20comprising%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Puducherry%20-%20had%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20qualifying%20candidates%20for%20JEE%20Advanced%20last%20year%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20in%202023%20too%2C%20there%20were%2010%2C432%20qualifying%20candidates%20from%20this%20zone%2C%20with%20174%20candidates%20featuring%20in%20the%20top%20500%20and%20six%20in%20the%20top%2010.%20The%20zone%20had%20the%20best%20gender%20ratio%20among%20all%20IIT%20campuses%2C%20with%20nearly%201%2C200%20girls%20joining%20tech%20colleges%20last%20year.%20The%20proportion%20of%20female%20aspirants%20is%20also%20high%20-%20almost%20at%20par%20with%20males.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20traditional%20subjects%2C%20IITs%20are%20also%20working%20on%20introducing%20diverse%20programmes%20like%20public%20policy%20and%20design.%20All%20these%20steps%20reflect%20the%20resolve%20to%20ease%20the%20journey%20to%20IIT%20for%20the%20female%20student.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718261880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%