%20and%20students%20started%20raising%20questions%20on%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20demanding%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fexplainer-what-is-the-controversy-surrounding-neet-ug-2024-results-5838160%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20What%20Is%20The%20Controversy%20Surrounding%20NEET%20UG%202024%20Results%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pradhan%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20all%20the%20allegations%20against%20NTA.%20%26quot%3BAllegations%20of%20corruption%20in%20NTA%20unfounded%2C%20and%20the%20testing%20agency%20is%20a%20credible%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20minister%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwenty%20four%20lakh%20students%20appear%20in%20the%20examination.%20A%20hearing%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20underway%20today%20and%20this%20issue%20is%20regarding%20around%201%2C500%20students.%20The%20government%20is%20ready%20to%20give%20answers%20to%20the%20court.%20This%20specific%20issue%20is%20being%20taken%20into%20consideration%20and%20a%20committee%20of%20academicians%20has%20been%20formed.%20The%20government%20will%20present%20this%20in%20front%20of%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%2C%20the%20minister%20assures%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20action%20against%20the%20people%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examination%20was%20held%20on%20May%205%20across%204%2C750%20centres.%20The%20allegations%20such%20as%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20the%20grant%20of%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20aspirants%20led%20to%20protests%20and%20filing%20of%20cases%20in%20seven%20high%20courts%20as%20also%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENTA%20denied%20any%20irregularities%20and%20said%20the%20changes%20made%20in%20the%20NCERT%20textbooks%20and%20grace%20marks%20for%20losing%20time%20at%20the%20examination%20centres%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20students%20scoring%20higher%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718260440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdmr0n3jg_dharmendra-pradhan_625x300_02_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fno-student-will-face-any-disadvantage-union-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-neet-row-5880050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reacting%20to%20the%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%2C%20the%20minister%20assures%20that%20the%20government%20will%20take%20action%20against%20the%20people%20responsible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fno-student-will-face-any-disadvantage-union-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-neet-row-5880050%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fno-student-will-face-any-disadvantage-union-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-neet-row-5880050%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fno-student-will-face-any-disadvantage-union-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-neet-row-5880050%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riots%20break%20out%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%20over%20President%20Javier%20Milei's%20reforms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718260020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F06%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-argentina-buenos-aires_6580214.jpg%3F20240613071514%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Friots-break-out-in-buenos-aires-over-president-javier-mileis-reforms-13152320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20people%20rallied%20outside%20Congress%20in%20Argentina's%20capital%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%20to%20protest%20against%20a%20bill%20proposed%20by%20President%20Javier%20Milei.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%