%20foundation%20day%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20founded%20by%20her%20father%2C%20the%20Baramati%20MP%20said%20as%20the%20NDA%20holds%20its%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20it%20should%20grant%20full%20loan%20waiver%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20UPA%20regime%2C%20the%20NCP%20worked%20as%20an%20ally%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Manmohan%20ji%20showed%20trust%20and%20love%20towards%20Pawar%20saheb%2C%20and%20he%20got%20two%20and%20a%20half%20cabinet%20berths%20although%20the%20party%20had%20only%20eight%20or%20nine%20MPs%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20did%20not%20think%20about%20numbers%20and%20respected%20the%20party%20as%20its%20ally%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20government%20also%2C%20everyone%20treated%20each%20other%20with%20respect.%20We%20did%20not%20stick%20to%20any%20formula.%20Our%20relationship%20was%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%20and%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20said%20she%20was%20not%20surprised%20that%20the%20NCP%20did%20not%20get%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20observed%20from%20close%20quarters%20how%20they%20(BJP)%20treated%20their%20allies%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20Their%20approach%20is%20not%20of%20'one%20size%20fits%20all'%20(equal%20treatment)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20said%20the%20NCP%20wanted%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20had%20declined%20the%20BJP's%20offer%20of%20minister%20of%20state%20(MoS)%20with%20independent%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20NCP%20%26quot%3Bwas%20ready%20to%20wait%26quot%3B%20but%20wanted%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCP%2C%20part%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20along%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20performed%20poorly%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20(Raigad)%20from%20the%20four%20it%20contested.%20It%20also%20lost%20the%20prestige%20battle%20in%20Baramati%2C%20where%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20wife%2C%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20was%20trounced%20by%20sitting%20MP%20Sule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20NDA's%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20Ms%20Sule%20said%20the%20government%20should%20grant%20full%20loan%20waiver%20to%20farmers.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20they%20give%20this%20country%20a%20stable%20government.%20I%20expect%20a%20decision%20on%20loan%20waiver%20and%20commodities%20like%20onion%20and%20milk%20prices%20as%20farmers%20are%20under%20tremendous%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718007660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flbf1dv0g_ajit-pawar-supriya-sule_625x300_07_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-no-cabinet-berth-for-ajit-pawar-led-ncp-cousin-supriya-sules-stinger-5857551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20on%20Monday%20said%20she%20was%20not%20surprised%20that%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20did%20not%20get%20a%20berth%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20new%20cabinet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-no-cabinet-berth-for-ajit-pawar-led-ncp-cousin-supriya-sules-stinger-5857551%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-no-cabinet-berth-for-ajit-pawar-led-ncp-cousin-supriya-sules-stinger-5857551%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A