%3E(field%20boundary)%20wall%20higher%20so%20that%20chemical%20water%20from%20neighbouring%20fields%20does%20not%20seep%20into%20your%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20received%20immense%20recognition%20for%20their%20work.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20they%20were%20awarded%20by%20the%20Agriculture%20University%20of%20Sirmour.%20On%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%20in%202022%2C%20they%20were%20honoured%20by%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Sirmaur%2C%20IAS%20Sumit%20Khimta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20small%20farmers%20who%20are%20receiving%20so%20much%20recognition.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20achievement%20for%20us.%20We%20never%20knew%20we%20would%20get%20opportunities%20to%20address%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20front%20of%20the%20officials%20like%20the%20governor%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaswinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20recognition%2C%20Jaswinder%20takes%20pride%20in%20receiving%20compliments%20from%20her%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20if%20I%20ignored%20the%20%3Cem%3Ephulke%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wheat%20chapati)%20for%20some%20time%2C%20they%20would%20harden%20and%20dry%20out.%20But%20those%20prepared%20from%20the%20naturally%20grown%20wheat%20remain%20soft.%20We%20get%20lots%20of%20praise%20from%20guests%20for%20the%20taste%20and%20aroma%20of%20our%20chapati%20and%20vegetables.%20When%20asked%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20the%20magic%20behind%20it%20is%20natural%20farming!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ranjit%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717146517000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351525%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20Jaswinder%20Kaur%20and%20Ranjit%20Singh%20from%20Himachal%20have%20