0Menstrual%20Cups%2C%20Offers%20Regional%20Language%20Training%20On%20How%20To%20Use%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERemember%20when%20as%20a%20young%20girl%20you%20had%20just%20started%20to%20menstruate%2C%20the%20biggest%20concern%20was%20if%20we%20stained%20our%20clothes.%20A%20secret%20code%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20was%20developed%20and%20passed%20to%20best%20friends%20or%20any%20other%20female%20to%20check%20if%20there%20was%20a%20leakage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20inconvenience%20becomes%20more%20bearable%20with%20age%2C%20the%20horror%20of%20staining%20continues%20for%20most%20of%20our%20lives.%20This%20is%20a%20familiar%20story%20to%20any%20woman%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20same%20for%20Ira%20Guha%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Asan%2C%20a%20menstrual%20cup%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20be%20quite%20athletic%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20run%20around.%20I%20loved%20being%20outdoors%20and%20was%20an%20active%20basketball%20player%20in%20my%20school.%20I%20remember%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337583%2Ftulsi-village-chhattisgarh-youtube-village-hummer-studios-being-chhattisgarhiya-alwa-jalwa-gold-cg04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20in%20Chhattisgarh%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20state-level%20game%20and%20being%20on%20my%20period.%20There%20were%20no%20bins%20in%20the%20school%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20the%20soiled%20pad%20in%20my%20bag%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20feeling%20disgusted%20and%20embarrassed%20all%20day%20are%20some%20of%20her%20core%20experiences%20that%20shaped%20her%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20menstrual%20hygiene%20business%2C%20she%20says.%20With%20her%20company%20Asan%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20switch%20to%20menstrual%20cups%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cup%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20periods%20comfortable%20for%20every%20woman.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20menstrual%20cups%20can%20help%20make%20periods%20easier%20and%20healthier%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20Asan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20when%20she%20was%2018%20to%20pursue%20her%20higher%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%20in%20London%20and%20kept%20visiting%20home%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%20In%202016-17%2C%20the%20movie%20Padman%20was%20getting%20very%20popular%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20around%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20visits%20during%20this%20time%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20that%20our%20cook%20was%20on%20leave%20and%20I%20had%20called%20to%20ask%20the%20reason.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20a%20rash%20due%20to%20using%20cheap%20sanitary%20pads.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurious%2C%20Ira%20asked%20her%20to%20bring%20the%20pad%20once%20she%20recovered%20to%20check%20its%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20never%20imagine%20using%20that%20pad%2C%20as%20it%20was%20very%20harsh%20and%20the%20material%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20absorbent.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20time%20that%20I%20introduced%20her%20to%20menstrual%20cups.%20I%20was%20using%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20but%20there%20were%20no%20brands%20at%20the%20time%20selling%20them%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%2